    content: "Carmen Perea (f) holds a technical degree in Computer sciences, she also holds a PMP Project Management Certification. In 2000, she joined ATOS (currently Eviden) and worked in the Insurance sector as functional analyst working in projects for relevant Spanish Insurance companies , since 2009 she worked in the ATOS Research and Innovation Team, she have participated in several Research and innovation National consultancy projects and in European projects, Currently, she led the Transport Systems and Urban Mobility Unit in Eviden Research and Innovation, she is the GreenMov Project coordinator.", linkedin: "https://www.linkedin.com/in/carmen-perea-escribano-7a001613/", twitter: "", domain: "", location: "",
