    content: "Matic Serc is the founder and Director at eVineyrad/eOrchard (Elmibit d.o.o.), provider of IT for Agriculture to vineyard and orchard management organizations on 5 continents. He has 8+ years working experience ranging from Technical Development, Product Management, Leading IT projects and more, for Agricultural organizations (farms, companies, holdings).", linkedin: "https://www.linkedin.com/in/maticserc/", twitter: "", domain: "", location: "",
