    content: "John Wood holds a degree in electronic engineering from De Montfort University (Leicester, UK). After working for 10 years in real-time embedded firmware development he has forged a 20+ year career in worldwide sales and business development in the telecoms and security sectors, in companies such as Siemens, Scati and now Libelium, a leading IoT solution manufacturer with projects deployed worldwide. John engages with stakeholders and channel partners in the North American market to discuss how Libelium’s IoT solutions can help to solve problems in the Environmental and Smart City domains, with the objective of improving sustainability, efficiency and quality of life.", linkedin: "https://www.linkedin.com/in/johndavidwood/", twitter: "", domain: "", location: "",
